title: New Delhi: Dr. A.P.J. Abdul Kalam Technical University has released the UPTAC Round 2 Seat Allotment List on September 22, 2023. Candidates can check their allotment status on the official website at uptac.admissions.nic.in.
description: Following the schedule, applicants who have been selected under the UPTAC Round 2 Counselling 2023 need to complete their payment for the seats between September 22 – 24, 2023. Candidates who are allotted seats have to pay the confirmation fee for UPTAC round 2 seat allotment. Accordingly, they will have to submit their choices against UPTAC seat allotment through freeze & float options. Know how to fill choices for UPTAC Counselling 2023 in this article below!

title: New Delhi: NTA has released an official calendar with the exam dates of several of its national entrance exams. As per the schedule, the NEET UG Exam Date is May 5, 2024, to offer admission to the medical, paramedical, dental and AYUSH courses.
description: The National Testing Agency (NTA) will announce the registration dates and official notification for each exam separately soon. An official statement from NTA also states that The registration dates for the JEE (Main) are likely to be announced early next week.”NTA Official Examination Calendar
